Notes: Grab counted as displacement, but not CC, because animation length is basically the same as the stun.
E knockback is counted as displacement but not CC.  His CC is a fear.
I decided to include roots as hard CC.
Quinn has a tiny knockback on E which I am not counting.
Rammus has a tiny knockback on Q which I did count; the difference is animation time.
Skarner's ult can move enemies, but is not a displacement effect.
Ult moves target, but is not a displacement effect.
